---
description: CLI and TUI display standards
globs:
  - "src/agent/cli.c"
  - "src/agent/tui.c"
---

- Include `human/design_tokens.h` for all display constants
- Colors: `HU_COLOR_ACCENT`, `HU_COLOR_SUCCESS`, `HU_COLOR_ERROR`, `HU_COLOR_WARNING`, `HU_COLOR_INFO`, `HU_COLOR_MUTED` — never hardcode `\033[...m` ANSI sequences
- Box drawing: `HU_BOX_VERT`, `HU_BOX_HORIZ`, `HU_BOX_TL`, `HU_BOX_TR`, `HU_BOX_BL`, `HU_BOX_BR` — never hardcode UTF-8 byte sequences
- Symbols: `HU_CHEVRON` for prompt, `HU_CHECK` for success, `HU_CROSS` for failure
- Reset: always use `HU_COLOR_RESET` after colored output
- Bold/dim: `HU_COLOR_BOLD`, `HU_COLOR_DIM`
